Hi all, I had tooth ache and just went for consultation regarding it, and to my surprise I had to get two wisdom teeth extracted. Well, Dr. Chetan, Dr. Abhishek and Dr. Nada did a tremendous and painless job. I'm very much thankful to their observation and the job they did with my teeth.

context: RCT - Root Canal Treatment,
review:
Dr. Abhishek helped me with my tooth pain which was gone in first sitting itself. He was very friendly, ************ *** supportive. I had to go for 3 appointments and he was so positive every time I came that it made me feel very comfortable and welcomed.
He is definitely me and my family doctor from now onwards! 
It is very important to go to a good dentist for treatment, and I would highly recommend Abhishek sir for anyone who is reading this.
